OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FThe Three Lions will kick off their
OL,7,FFifa World Cup journey on June 17,
OL,8,Fwith their first game against Croatia
OL,9,Fin the searing heat in Dallas, Texas.
OL,11,FIt will be the team's first test in
OL,12,Fwhat climate experts are saying will
OL,13,Fbe a challenging competition for many
OL,14,Fplayers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
