OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FSo how hot will it get - and how will
OL,7,Fthis affect the athletes? ITV News
OL,8,Fexplains.
OL,10,FWhat are the expected temperatures?
OL,12,FThe "seasonal temperature outlook" for
OL,13,Fthe US, compiled by the National
OL,14,FWeather Service, suggests every part
OL,15,Fof the country will experience
OL,16,Ftemperatures above the historical
OL,17,Faverage in June and July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
