OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FHot weather is also predicted for
OL,7,FMexico, where children will finish
OL,8,Fschool six weeks earlier this year due
OL,9,Fto an "extreme heat wave".
OL,11,FThe country has already experienced
OL,12,Fmultiple heat records this year, with
OL,13,Fthe north-western city of Hermosillo
OL,14,Freaching 42 degrees Celcius in March.
OL,16,FOut of the 104 games taking place, 13
OL,17,Fare taking place in Mexico - in
OL,18,FGuadalajara, Mexico City and Monterrey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
