OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FIn Canada, where 13 games will be
OL,7,Fhosted, the weather is a bit more
OL,8,Fmoderate, with temperatures ranging
OL,9,Ffrom 20 to 25 degrees Celcius.
OL,11,FAre there any other extreme weather
OL,12,Fevents to be worried about?
OL,14,FPoor air quality from wildfires, which
OL,15,Fare common in the region during the
OL,16,Fsummer months, could also have an
OL,17,Fimpact on the tournament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
