OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FAcross the US, wildfire activity has
OL,7,Falready hit historic levels this
OL,8,Fspring and is likely to worsen in the
OL,9,Fcoming months, experts say.
OL,11,FSince the beginning of the year, there
OL,12,Fhave been nearly 30,000 fires across
OL,13,Fthe country - the most in almost two
OL,14,Fdecades.
OL,16,FSummer thunderstorms are also common,
OL,17,Fparticularly in warm and humid cities
OL,18,Fsuch as Miami, Houston and Atlanta.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
