PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FIf lightning is detected within 10
OL,7,Fmiles of a stadium, the US official
OL,8,Frecommendation and standard practice
OL,9,Fis that play is suspended until 30
OL,10,Fminutes after the last lightning
OL,11,Fstrike.
OL,13,FWhat is Fifa doing about the weather
OL,14,Fand will games be cancelled?
OL,16,FSimilar to other sporting bodies, Fifa
OL,17,Fuses "wet bulb globe temperature"
OL,18,F(WBGT) as a measurement to define
OL,19,Fwhether a game should go ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
