PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FWBGT takes into account not just the
OL,7,Ftemperature, but also humidity,
OL,8,Fradiant heat (direct sunlight) and
OL,9,Fwind speed.
OL,11,FUnder Fifa rules, if WBGT measurements
OL,12,Freach 32 C before a match,
OL,13,Fconsideration should be given to
OL,14,Fsuspending it.
OL,16,FPreliminary research, published in The
OL,17,FGuardian, shows that WBGT could exceed
OL,18,F32 C in Dallas - where England is
OL,19,Fplaying one of their group-stage
OL,20,Fmatches - as well as Houston and
OL,21,FMonterrey in Mexico.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FSeveral football governing bodies,
OL,7,Fincluding the global players' union
OL,8,FFifpro, consider a WBGT above 28 C to
OL,9,Fbe a threshold where matches should
OL,10,Fpotentially be delayed or postponed.
OL,12,FA report, published by Football for
OL,13,FFuture and Common Goal, also found
OL,14,Fthat 10 of the 16 venues hosting the
OL,15,FWorld Cup are at very high risk of
OL,16,Fexperiencing extreme heat stress
OL,17,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
