OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FFifa organisers are trying to adapt to
OL,7,Fthe heat by introducing more evening
OL,8,Fmatches as well as mandatory three-
OL,9,Fminute cooling breaks in each half of
OL,10,Fa game.
OL,12,FOther welfare plans include allowing
OL,13,Fteams the usual of up to five
OL,14,Fsubstitutions, a minimum of three rest
OL,15,Fdays between matches, and staff and
OL,16,Fsubstitutes will have access to
OL,17,Fclimate-controlled benches at outdoor
OL,18,Fmatches.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
