PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FHowever, most stadiums are open-air,
OL,7,Fleaving players and millions of fans
OL,8,Fexposed to peak summer heat.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FHow will this impact players?
OL,17,FExtreme heat puts players and fans at
OL,18,Frisk of heat-related illness,
OL,19,Fincluding nausea, dehydration,
OL,20,Fheadaches, strokes, and even death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
