OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FIt can also affect soccer players'
OL,7,Fperformance, with studies showing that
OL,8,Fplayers cover less distance, perform
OL,9,Ffewer high-intensity sprints and get
OL,10,Ftired more quickly in extreme
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FExhausted players are also more prone
OL,14,Fto injuries, while hotter matches have
OL,15,Fbeen linked to more penalty shootouts,
OL,16,Fas exhausted teams struggle to break
OL,17,Feach other down in extra time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FSome players have already publicly
OL,7,Faddressed their concerns over the
OL,8,Fweather, including Norwegian
OL,9,Fmidfielder Morten Thorsby, who said
OL,10,F"it's an obvious problem" that impacts
OL,11,Fperformance on the pitch.
OL,13,F"Obviously, the intensity of the game
OL,14,Fgoes down," Thorsby said.
OL,16,F"Football is also an entertainment
OL,17,Findustry. The spectacle and the show
OL,18,Fand the sport loses its value if the
OL,19,Fplayers are not able to perform at
OL,20,Ftheir best."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781608794
OL,3,CCould extreme weather affect the Fifa
OL,4,CWorld Cup - and how will players cope?
OL,6,FHe is among a group of current and
OL,7,Fformer professional footballers who
OL,8,Fhave written to football's world
OL,9,Fgoverning body, calling for better
OL,10,Fmeasures to protect players.
OL,12,FA Fifa spokesperson said: "Fifa is
OL,13,Fcommitted to protecting the health and
OL,14,Fsafety of players, referees, fans,
OL,15,Fvolunteers and staff."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
